In class twenty-five, Tammy finally accepted my suggestions that she
make a procedure to rpint out all her stories on one piece of paper.  I
did all the typing for the procedure, FOXYLADY, and inserted the story
titles and spacing.  Tammy told me the order in which she wanted the
